title: Tobruk to Tarakan
creator_credit: Australian Commonwealth Film Unit, Australia. Repatriation Dept. and Frank Bagnall
brief_description: Presents a chronological study of the Australian Army’s involvement in the various theatres of WWII: Greece, Crete, Syria, Tobruk, Alamein, Pacific, New Guinea, Taraken. Archival footage from Australian War Memorial.
